n, c, d = map(int, input().split())
    fountains = []
    for i in range(n):
        b, p, t = map(str, input().split())
        b = int(b)
        p = int(p)
        if t == "C":
            fountains.append((b, p))
        else:
            fountains.append((b, p * d))
    fountains.sort(key=lambda x: x[0], reverse=True)
    fountains.sort(key=lambda x: x[1])
    if fountains[0][1] + fountains[1][1] > c:
        print(0)
    else:
        print(fountains[0][0] + fountains[1][0])

n = int(input())
    x = []
    y = []
    for i in range(n):
        x_i, y_i = map(int, input().split())
        x.append(x_i)
        y.append(y_i)
    count = 0
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(i+1, n):
            if (x[i] - x[j])**2 + (y[i] - y[j])**2 == (x[i] - x[j])**2 + (y[i] - y[j])**2:
                count += 1
    print(count)

                count += 1

if not root:
            return []
        self.dic = {}
        self.max_freq = 0
        self.helper(root)
        return [k for k, v in self.dic.items() if v == self.max_freq]

    def helper(self, root):
        if not root:
            return 0
        left = self.helper(root.left)
        right = self.helper(root.right)
        total = left + right + root.val
        self.dic[total] = self.dic.get(total, 0) + 1
        self.max_freq = max(self.max_freq, self.dic[total])
        return total
